423
00:21:19,261 --> 00:21:20,361
If we're going to contact them,

424
00:21:20,361 --> 00:21:23,761
let's do so after we revive the message.

425
00:21:23,761 --> 00:21:25,261
If the letters were written with blood,

426
00:21:25,261 --> 00:21:29,161
