00:24:07,161 --> 00:24:10,761
What? From Shinichi?

455
00:24:10,761 --> 00:24:14,161
What a thing to be talking about at a murder site.

456
00:24:14,161 --> 00:24:16,461
Ikuro didn't pick up the baumkuchen

457
00:24:16,461 --> 00:24:19,461
with the poison on it by accident.

458
00:24:19,461 --> 00:24:21,861
We checked your slipper

